How to use:
===========

Simply run `python RG.py`

Dependencies:
=============

- pygtk2 (can be disabled)
- python-BeautifulSoup
- something for watching mms flux (gstreamer based video player, mplayer,
  mimms, ...)

How to disabled PyGtk:
======================

If you are a real man, you can just delete the last line of this script
(starting at GTK stuff ... import pygtk) and only use the cli() function).
More information with online python documentation.

Motivation:
===========

I am allergic to SilverLight technology and the latest Fedora 13 broke video
streaming with {totem,parole}-mozlugin.
